title: Agent_2000_Die_Laksman
description: South Africa does it's own version of James Bond, with a school boy as the hero. Secret superhero Agent 2000, a 14 year old boy, is running short on time. He needs to unmask the school bully AKA 'Die Laksman' / The Executioner before the end of the school's initiation period, or the school's principal will be fired, his reputation as a secret agent will be gone, and he will lose both his best friend and the girl of his dreams. Will he outwit The Executioner in time, or will Agent 2000 be The Executioner's ultimate victim?
